EDWIN C. M. DICKEY v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 47558. Decided July 11, 1949. Mr. Edwin O. M. Dichey pro se. Mr. W. W. Fleming, with whom was Mr. Assistant Attorney General H. G. Morison, for the defendant.

Plaintiif’s petition for writ of certiorari denied January 9,1950.

Plaintiff’s motion for new trial overruled October 3, 1949] *
